### ğŸ” KQL Query Used
```kql
let StartDate = datetime(2025-12-01);
let EndDate = datetime(2025-12-05);

DeviceEvents
| where ActionType == "SensitiveFileRead"
| where DeviceName == "main1-srvr"
| where FileName contains "bonus"
